{
  "stem": "17526.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 251.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I tried-- a cousin of mine who is in Israel now, the two of us were marching, and we were in the front of the columns, in back.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We were slowing down and-- it wasn't just a marching, it was just walking with-- with wrapped around paper sacks on our shoes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Fierce cold and-- and-- and in the middle of nowhere, on open highways, open roads.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we were trying to play dead.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So we sort of backed up, and we were trying to at the end.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we laid down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But as we tried to play the thing, we saw they were shooting some people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Now, this one [? thing, ?] I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I-- I can't talk about it, either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "A father and son were walking and the father was just on his last leg, literally he could not walk.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And he fell in the snow, and he was-- he was just croaking.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "You could see his face, [? open mouth. ?] And the son was pulling him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He says, Papa, he says, you made it this far, we don't have too far to walk.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Come on, I'll help you get up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And this-- the man is laying in the snow and the German came over with his rifle, and he hit the son over the head and he says, if you're not leaving him, you're not marching.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I'll shoot you and I'll shoot him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I watched and the son left his father dying in the snow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "This is so impregnate-- imprinted and impregnated in my mind so bad that every time I talk about the scenes, I see the son walking away, leaving his father in the snow being shot by a German freezing in the snow.",
      "word_count": 41
    }
  ],
